title: FrietHoes
typeOfFood: Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Belgian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Tiny biological fry shop. Uses a blend of 5 oils (palm oil plus other vegetable oils) to fry the potatoes. Belgian style twice-fried fries. The mayonaise is not veg-friendly, but the peanutsauce is vegan.
